title: Best of The Herd: 10/14/2019
itunes:title: Best of The Herd: 10/14/2019
description:
Colin is not as concerned with the Cowboys as everyone else and explains why. He is not surprised by the browns struggles because everyone who doesn't live in Ohio saw this coming for Baker and the Browns. He explains where he was right and wrong over the weekend including a rough week for the Blazing 5. Plus, Super Bowl Champion QB Trent Dilfer talks with Colin about the Eagles awful performance and why Deshaun Watson's success is not a surprise to him.
